  \begin {tikzcd}
  C/x\ar [rr, bend left=50, "\Sigma _f", ""{name=L}]\ar [rr, bend right=50,
  "\Pi _f"', ""{name=R}] && C/y\ar [ll,
  "f^*", near start]\ar [ll, phantom, ""{name=f}]\makebox [0pt][l]{.}
  \ar [phantom, from=L, to=f]{}{\bot }
  \ar [phantom, from=f, to=R]{}{\bot }
  \end {tikzcd}

We define \Sigma _f by direct composition with f: 




